<section>
  <h2>Purpose</h2>
  <p>
    Reports produced by Hidden Insight Labs are designed to make performance,
    usability, and risk visible in systems where standard QA processes do not
    yet apply.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Typical Contents</h2>
  <ul class="pillars">
    <li>Testing context and methodology</li>
    <li>Observed usability issues</li>
    <li>Technical constraints and edge cases</li>
    <li>Risk assessment</li>
    <li>Recommendations and next steps</li>
  </ul>
</section>

